snippet.title: The Foglands - VR Gameplay & FPS Mode Reveal. (PS5, PSVR2, Quest 2)
snippet.description:
Pre-order on PlayStation now!
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10003574/

The Foglands is an atmospheric 3D roguelike shooter that is playable on both VR and non-VR in first-person mode.

Coming October 31st, 2023 to the PlayStation and Quest Store
